& \frac{b+1}{a+b+1}+\frac{c+1}{b+c+1}+\frac{a+1}{c+a+1} \\
& \quad \geq \frac{(a+b+c+3)^{2}}{(b+1)(a+b+1)+(c+1)(b+c+1)+(a+1)(c+a+1)}=2
\end{aligned}
$$

Equality holds iff $a=b=c=1$.

