$$

Also $(x+y+z)^{2} \geq 3(x y+y z+z x)$, so we deduce
$$
p=x+y+z \geq \sqrt{3(4-x y z)} \stackrel{(3)}{\geq} \sqrt{3(4-1)}=3 .
$$

Finally by using (2) we obtain that $3 p^{2}-7 q-6 \geq 0$, i.e. inequality (1) holds.

