& =\frac{x(y+z)+y(x+z)+z(x+y)}{(x+y)(y+z)(z+x)} \\
& =\frac{2}{(x+y)(y+z)(z+x)} \tag{1}
\end{align*}
$$

It is easy to show that
$$
