$$
\begin{aligned}
\sum a b\left(a^{2}+b^{2}\right) & =\sum \frac{a^{4}+b^{4}+6 a^{2} b^{2}-(a-b)^{4}}{4}= \\
& =\frac{3 \sum a^{4}+6 \sum a^{2} b^{2}-\sum(a-b)^{4}}{4}=\frac{3-\sum(a-b)^{4}}{4} \leq \frac{3}{4}
\end{aligned}
$$

