Furthermore
$$
\begin{equation*}
\sqrt{1-a}-\sqrt{a}=\frac{(\sqrt{1-a}-\sqrt{a})(\sqrt{1-a}+\sqrt{a})}{\sqrt{1-a}+\sqrt{a}}=\frac{1-2 a}{\sqrt{1-a}+\sqrt{a}} \tag{2}
\end{equation*}
