T[2,1,0]+\frac{1}{6} T[1,1,1] \leq \frac{7}{27}\left(\frac{1}{2} T[3,0,0]+3 T[2,1,0]+T[1,1,1]\right)
$$
i.e.
$$
\begin{equation*}
12 T[2,1,0] \leq 7 T[3,0,0]+5 T[1,1,1] \tag{1}
