& \quad \Leftrightarrow \quad \frac{x^{3}}{x^{3}+(y+z)^{3}} \geq \frac{x^{4}}{\left(x^{2}+y^{2}+z^{2}\right)^{2}} \\
& \quad \Leftrightarrow \quad 2 x^{2}\left(y^{2}+z^{2}\right)+\left(y^{2}+z^{2}\right)^{2} \geq x(y+z)^{3} \tag{2}
\end{align*}
$$

By $A M \leq Q M$ we have
