& \sqrt{\frac{a^{3}}{a^{3}+(b+c)^{3}}}+\sqrt{\frac{a^{3}}{a^{3}+(b+c)^{3}}}+\sqrt{\frac{a^{3}}{a^{3}+(b+c)^{3}}} \\
& \quad \geq \frac{a^{2}}{a^{2}+b^{2}+c^{2}}+\frac{b^{2}}{a^{2}+b^{2}+c^{2}}+\frac{c^{2}}{a^{2}+b^{2}+c^{2}}=1
