$$

Recalling Nesbitt's inequality we have
$$
\begin{equation*}
\frac{a}{b+c}+\frac{b}{c+a}+\frac{c}{a+b} \geq \frac{3}{2} \tag{2}
\end{equation*}
$$

From (1) and (2) we obtain the required inequality.

