Let $\frac{1998}{1998+x_{i}}=a_{i}$. The problem reduces to proving that for any positive real numbers $a_{1}, a_{2}, \ldots, a_{n}$ such that $a_{1}+a_{2}+\cdots+a_{n}=1$ we have the inequality

