$$

Furthermore
$$
(a+b+c)^{2}=a^{2}+b^{2}+c^{2}+2(a b+b c+c a) \geq 3(a b+b c+c a)=3
$$
i.e.
$$
\begin{equation*}
a+b+c \geq \sqrt{3} \tag{2}
