$$

Using (1) and (2) we obtain the required inequality.
Equality occurs iff $a=b=c=1 / \sqrt{3}$.

Since $0 \leq a, b, c \leq 1$ it follows that $0 \leq a^{3}, b^{3}, c^{3} \leq 1$, so we have
$$
