\end{aligned}
$$
i.e.
$$
\begin{equation*}
\frac{(a+b+c+d+e+f)^{2}}{S} \geq 3 \tag{4}
\end{equation*}
$$

Finally from (1) and (4) we obtain the required inequality.
Equality occurs iff $a=b=c=d=e=f$.

