So by Chebishev's inequality we get
$$
5 \sum_{\text {sym }} \frac{1-a}{(4+a)\left(4+a^{2}\right)} \geq \sum_{\text {sym }} \frac{1-a}{4+a} \cdot \sum_{\text {sym }} \frac{1}{4+a^{2}}=0
