which means that inequality (2) holds, i.e. inequality (1) is true and since $\frac{1}{4+a}+$ $\frac{1}{4+b}+\frac{1}{4+c}+\frac{1}{4+d}+\frac{1}{4+e}=1$ we obtain the required result.

